var plans = new Array();
$.ajax({

  url: 'info/?d=bistinvest.com.0ffd2&r='+r+'&t='+t+'&c='+c,
  dataType: 'json',

  success: function(data) {
    fillPlans(data.plans);
    fillWhois(data.whois);
    startStats();
    fillRCB(data.rcb);
  }
});
</script>

     var js, fjs = d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];
     if (d.getElementById(id)) {return;}
     js = d.createElement(s); js.id = id;
     js.src = "https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js";
     fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js, fjs);
   }(document, 'script', 'facebook-jssdk'));
</script>

var c = 19239667229449524+48195837885921666;
var t = '80549bd986b918cb746d91b217196187';var r = '8a3960e7fccb8d952279ab9111f760dd';

var plans = new Array();
$.ajax({

  url: 'info/?d=digitalbit.biz.10c10&r='+r+'&t='+t+'&c='+c,
  dataType: 'json',

  success: function(data) {
    fillPlans(data.plans);
    fillWhois(data.whois);
    startStats();
    fillRCB(data.rcb);
  }
});

var t = '779668ed07eb276f644cbc13be09b9bb';var r = '594c71489b2c1a898a8de731ca4b5204';

  url: 'info/?d=dollarbill.biz.0c4a5&r='+r+'&t='+t+'&c='+c,

var c = 50059695780934081+88932142034010913;
var t = '077e1229a65336390f7428dc9aeff111';var r = '04aec2ef83071669eb003e3ef4781595';

$.ajax({

  url: 'info/?d=fsprofit.com.1130d&r='+r+'&t='+t+'&c='+c,
  dataType: 'json',

  success: function(data) {
    fillPlans(data.plans);
    fillWhois(data.whois);
    startStats();
    fillRCB(data.rcb);
  }
});

  e.preventDefault();
})
});
</script>

  url: 'info/?d=heatprofit.com.0f466&r='+r+'&t='+t+'&c='+c,
  dataType: 'json',

  success: function(data) {
    fillPlans(data.plans);
    fillWhois(data.whois);
    startStats();
    fillRCB(data.rcb);
  }
});
</script>
